Dependencies

R version

This package was developed using R version 4.5.2 (2025-10-31 ucrt).

  • lifecycle : 1.0.5
  • rlang : 1.1.7

  • spdep : 1.4-1

  • class : 7.3-23
  • tidygraph : 1.3.1

* Note that as of 2026-02-13 h3 package is not available on CRAN for R version 4.5.2. To install h3 please use remotes::install_github("crazycapivara/h3-r") or refer to h3-r GitHub.

Recommended packages for workflows

terra, sf, ggplot2, RColorBrewer, exactextractr
